rows.label: qst002207_msg0001
rows.name: U-um... are you Albina-san?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0002
rows.name: Mellica...?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0003
rows.name:
I never thought you'd
come to me yourself...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0004
rows.name:
I was just about to come
and get rid of you.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0005
rows.name: Get rid of me...?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0006
rows.name: D-do you mean... kill me?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0007
rows.name: Huh? You didn't realize?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0008
rows.name:
Is that why you hired that group
of Drivers to get to me first?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0009
rows.name:
N-no, that's not it...
These people are kind...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0010
rows.name:
I came because I wanted to
talk to you, Albina-san...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0011
rows.name: There's nothing to talk about!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0012
rows.name:
If it weren't for you... I would
have been in the Choir...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0013
rows.name:
Ah, it's so frustrating, so infuriating,
so frustrating, so infuriating! You
got in, and I... Damn it!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0014
rows.name:
If only you weren't here...
if you just disappeared... I
could get into the Choir...!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0015
rows.name:
I could have escaped this life and
lived a much wealthier one...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0016
rows.name:
I was going to make things
easier for my mom and dad...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0017
rows.name: In that case, even if you did this...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0018
rows.name:
Anyway, I want to
change this situation!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0019
rows.name: I'm a refugee from Invidia...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0020
rows.name:
I have some mercenary acquaintances... If I
get rid of you and get into the Choir, I can
easily get the money to hire them...!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0021
rows.name: They'll be paid on contingency...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0022
rows.name:
So, with that... you're
all going to disappear!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0023
rows.name: E-everyone, please help me!
